title: Video: Skint Eastwood – Arhuaco (Prod. by Eyedress)
content:
Eyedress is an artist that’s been gracing our pages more and more over the last 2 months or so. Since his debut EP, he’s been producing more and more beats that, excluding a few exceptions, haven’t really floated my boat. This new cut though, a collaboration with Skint Eastwood, is getting it right. Full to the brim with tactile, satisfying and ultimately completely non-descript sounds, it rides a cheeky little melody holding hands firmly with a fuck-load of crunch.

Just how i like it.

Skint Eastwood – Arhuaco (Prod. by Eyedress) from EYEDRESS on Vimeo.
